Build System:
 Arch Linux 3.18.6-1-ARCH (x86_64 GNU/Linux)
 gcc 4.9.3-4

Required Libraries:
 glibc 2.21-2

C standard:
 c++11

How to Build:
$ make                                  # Builds source
$ make test                             # Builds source and runs main method
$ g++ -Wall -std=c++11 src/* -o game.o  # Build manually

